SoV Era, well equipped tanks have ATK of 1500 and AC of 1400, best pet is epic. Begins to fall behind, gets chewed up and spit out by some encounters.<br>
SoL Era, well equipped tanks have ATK of 1800 and AC of 1700, best pet is epic. Becomes very situational in raids, cannot hit some high end mobs well at all, is often not summoned.<br>
PoP Era, tanks will eclipse 2100 ATK and 2000 AC. Our BEST pet is gonna remain the epic? <br>
<br>
A pet that was designed for a 1100 AC world CANNOT function in a world of 2000 AC. He will get chewed up and spit out by XP mobs. I can't chain the damn thing cuz of recast delay, so I rely every day more and more on my nukes.<br>
